title: Green Bay Packers
summary: The Green Bay Packers are a professional American football team based in Green Bay, Wisconsin. The Packers compete in the National Football League (NFL) as a member club of the National Football Conference (NFC) North division. It is the third-oldest franchise in the NFL, dating back to 1919,[11][12] and is the only non-profit, community-owned major league professional sports team based in the United States.[lower-alpha 1][13] Home games have been played at Lambeau Field since 1957.
